Class OperationConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.naturalis.geneious.OperationConfig
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Ab1FastaImportConfig, CsvImportConfig, SplitNameConfig
    public abstract class OperationConfig
extends Object
    Base class for objects capturing the user input and other configuration data for one of the plugin's operations. OperationConfig objects are generated from OperationOptions objects.
    Author:
    Ayco Holleman
